  "prompt": "Is MBA Guru, Kohat enclave, Delhi, a good coaching institute for CAT preparation?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2021, I don't have specific reviews or data about MBA Guru in Kohat Enclave, Delhi. When evaluating a coaching institute for CAT preparation, consider the following factors:\n\n1. **Faculty Experience**: Look for the qualifications and experience of the instructors. Experienced faculty can make a significant difference in understanding concepts.\n\n2. **Past Results**: Check the institute's track record regarding students' success in CAT and admissions to top-tier MBA programs.\n\n3. **Course Structure**: Assess whether the course covers all necessary topics comprehensively and offers practice materials, mock tests, and doubt-clearing sessions.\n\n4. **Student Reviews**: Look for recent reviews or testimonials from former or current students to gauge their experiences.\n\n5. **Batch Size**: Smaller batch sizes often allow for more personalized attention from instructors.\n\n6. **Location and Facilities**: Consider the convenience of the location and the facilities provided (like libraries, study areas, etc.).\n\n7. **Fee Structure**: Compare the fees with the offerings and other similar institutes to determine if it provides good value for money.\n\nIt is recommended to visit the institute, attend a demo class if possible, and talk to current students to get a better understanding of their programs. You may also look for updated reviews and ratings online for the latest information.",
